---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Chainlink SmartCon 2024 — AES" bodyClass="inner-page">

  <div class="container-fluid event-hero">
    <div class="event-hero-inner">
      <div class="event-hero-left">
        <div class="event-location">Hong Kong</div>
        <div class="event-title">Chainlink<br />SmartCon<br />2024</div>
        <div class="event-tagline">
          Positioned strategically during Hong Kong Fintech Week — a 4-day flagship event for 2,000 attendees and 30 sponsors, with 4 stages of content over 2 days preceded by a 2-day Hacker House for developers.
        </div>
        <div class="event-hero-photo">
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work1.png')"></div>
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work2.png')"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-hero-right">
        <div class="event-detail-card">
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Strategy</div>
            <p>Timing SmartCon alongside Hong Kong Fintech Week was a deliberate play to maximize reach across both the crypto-native and traditional finance audiences flooding the city. The 4-day format — 2 days of Hacker House followed by 2 days of main conference — gave developers a focused environment before the broader audience arrived.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Production</div>
            <p>Four stages of simultaneous content demanded precise scheduling and a tight production infrastructure. We leaned into Hong Kong's visual identity throughout the event design — neon signage, lanterns, and cultural motifs that grounded the experience in the city and gave attendees a sense of place.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Sponsor Experience</div>
            <p>With 30 sponsors on-site, the exhibit floor needed to feel premium and purposeful. We worked closely with each sponsor to ensure their presence complemented the overall aesthetic while giving each brand meaningful visibility and engagement opportunities across all 4 days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-gallery">
    <div class="event-gallery-inner">
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work3.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work5.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work7.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work9.png')"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-back">
    <div class="event-back-inner">
      <a href="/work" class="cr-btn white ex-padding">← Back to All Events</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
